to achieve the goals of a civil nation
成為公民主義的國家

5
00:00:18,699 --> 00:00:20,699
My house is small.
我的房子很小。

6
00:00:21,062 --> 00:00:23,062
It can be hard to breathe.
在裡面很難呼吸。

7
00:00:27,037 --> 00:00:29,528
So when I found that key,
當我找到這個鑰匙。

8
00:00:30,008 --> 00:00:31,498
I was curious.
我很好奇。

9
00:00:34,981 --> 00:00:39,073
Because I knew the key belonged to the big man
因為我知道這個鑰匙是屬於一個大男人的

10
00:00:41,093 --> 00:00:44,017
I knew it was for his big house.
我知道是他大房子的。

11
00:00:46,002 --> 00:00:48,002
I heard he was gone.
我聽說他不見了。

12
00:00:48,990 --> 00:00:50,823
And it was true. He was gone.
是真的。他不見了。

13
00:00:51,264 --> 00:00:52,783
The house was empty.
房子是空的。

14
00:00:52,983 --> 00:00:54,963
So I took a chance.
所以我逮到機會。

15
00:01:03,228 --> 00:01:06,404
You would've done the same.
你也會做同樣的事。

16
00:01:12,031 --> 00:01:13,409
Let me tell you.
讓我告訴你。

17
00:01:13,509 --> 00:01:15,991
It's a different world inside.
裡面是不同的世界。

18
00:01:17,026 --> 00:01:19,878
He's got everything he needs.
他擁有所有他所需要的的東西。

19
00:01:21,102 --> 00:01:22,361
And more
及更多的

20
00:01:55,018 --> 00:01:57,018
So why shouldn't he share?
那他幹嘛不分享?

21
00:02:03,918 --> 00:02:05,918
Can't he give me a little?
他不能給我一點嗎?

22
00:02:07,985 --> 00:02:10,217
Aren't I a good kid?
我不是乖小孩嗎?

23
00:02:10,317 --> 00:02:11,897
I deserve it.
我應該得到啊。

24
00:02:17,017 --> 00:02:21,587
With all that space, I could breathe.
有這些空間，我可以呼吸。

25
00:02:31,006 --> 00:02:34,231
I felt like I could move.
我覺得我可以隨意走動。

26
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:51,053
I felt like I could fly.
我覺得我可以飛。

27
00:03:13,018 --> 00:03:14,435
Who's there?
誰在那裡?

28
00:03:15,446 --> 00:03:16,618
There he is!
他在這!

29
00:03:16,778 --> 00:03:18,596
Get out!
走開!

30
00:03:30,011 --> 00:03:32,956
But that's not my house.
但這不是我的房子。

31
00:03:34,097 --> 00:03:36,943
And it never will be.
且永遠不是。

32
00:03:38,061 --> 00:03:40,061
So where do I go?
那我該去哪裡?

33
00:03:43,008 --> 00:03:45,008
Where can I breathe?
哪裡我可以呼吸?

34
00:04:01,838 --> 00:04:03,838
I guess...
我想...

35
00:04:04,338 --> 00:04:06,924
there are other rooms.
還有其他的房間。
